# kfv --------------------------------------------------------------------------

IMAPAccount kfv
Host mail.kfv.io
User kfv@kfv.io
PassCmd "pass email/kfv.io"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore kfv-remote
Account kfv

MaildirStore kfv-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path /usr/home/kfv/Mail/kfv/
Inbox /usr/home/kfv/Mail/kfv/Inbox

Channel kfv-inbox
Far :kfv-remote:"INBOX"
Near :kfv-local:"INBOX"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Channel kfv-drafts
Far :kfv-remote:"Drafts"
Near :kfv-local:"Drafts"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Channel kfv-sent
Far :kfv-remote:"Sent"
Near :kfv-local:"Sent"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Channel kfv-trash
Far :kfv-remote:"Trash"
Near :kfv-local:"Trash"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Channel kfv-junk
Far :kfv-remote:"Junk"
Near :kfv-local:"Junk"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Group kfv
Channel kfv-inbox
Channel kfv-drafts
Channel kfv-sent
Channel kfv-trash
Channel kfv-junk

